 on both myeloid and lymphoid cells such as CD14 and CD19 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Krivtsov2007"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The suggestion that MLL is initiated within a progenitor cell is in line
