 therapy, as well as in the treatment of a number of other disorders such
 as autoimmune, cardiac and vascular diseases 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Burt2008"

\end_inset

.
 Cancer stem cells are thought to be present in both leukaemias and solid
